OL,5, Hans-Georg Maassen was once in charge  
OL,6, of hunting down neo-Nazis in Germany.  
OL,8,FNow he is being investigated for       
OL,9,Fsuspected right-wing extremism by the  
OL,10,Fintelligence agency he headed until    
OL,11,F2018.                                  
OL,13,FMr Maassen has published a letter from 
OL,14,Fthe Office for the Protection of the   
OL,15,FConstitution (BfV) confirming that he  
OL,16,Fis under investigation.                
OL,18,FThe agency says it can't comment on    
OL,19,Findividual cases because of strict     
OL,20,Fpersonal data protection rules.        
